Testing Frequencies

Each of the determinands are tested with differing frequencies within each material type. This is visualized to better understand the differences between each material type.

Categorization

Each observation is categorized as either having an e. coli measurement greater or less than the water quality limit of 900 no/100mL.

water.ecoli$E.coli.C.MF.conform <- water.ecoli$E.coli.C.MF.no.100ml < 900

E. coli vs. each determinand

Each determinand is plotted against e. coli concentration

Chi-square test (existence and severity of collinearity)

F-G test (location of collinearity)

t-test (pattern of collinearity)
